<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="length-n">length <strong><em>n</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /leŋθ/    美 /leŋθ/  </p>
<p>[U] &amp; [C]</p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>长；长度：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>The Amazon River is close to 6,400 kilometres <strong>in length</strong>.
亚马孙河长约6 400千米。</p><footer>译林新必修③ – 1改</footer></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>The snake usually reaches <strong>a length of</strong> 100 cm. 
蛇一般可以长到100厘米长。</p></div>

<h4 id="2">2.★ <strong>(时间的) 长度：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>the probable <strong>length of</strong> Beijing Man's life
北京猿人的大概寿命</p><footer>外研⑦ – 6</footer></div>

<h2 id="_2">固定搭配</h2>
<h3 id="at-length">at length</h3>
<p>1.<strong>最后；终于：</strong>  </p>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>At length, we began to understand what he wanted.
最后，我们开始明白他想要什么了。</p></div>

<p>2.★ <strong>长时间地；详尽地：</strong>  </p>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>I set up an interview with her and we discussed her project at length. 
我安排了与她会面，我们详细讨论了她的计划。</p><footer>2013 湖南</footer></div>

<h2 id="_3">派生词汇</h2>
<p>lengthen /'leŋθən/ v   </p></div>